Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
selectInstByCellName(25.10)                        selectInstByCellName(25.10)

Name
       selectInstByCellName  - Selects instances and hierarchical instances by
       cell name

Syntax
       selectInstByCellName

       [-help]

       <cellName>

       Selects instances and hierarchical instances by cell name. When hierar-
       chical instances are selected, child instances  are  also  highlighted.
       You can use this command after importing the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes the type and default
              information for each selectInstByCellName parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man selectInstByCellName

       <cellName>
              Specifies the name of the cell.

              Data_type: (libCell/ptnCell|vCell|topCell)+, required

Related Information
              * deselectInstByCellName

              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

